      "span_text": "Carotid artery injury was induced as described previously.  Briefly, the mice were anesthetized with halothane/N 2 O. By use of a dissecting microscope (MZ6, Leica), the bifurcation of the left carotid artery was exposed via a midline incision of the ventral side of the neck.",
